          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "刘清蒂本是我老身的名姓"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "望长官你与我盘查细问"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小师父，里面有一个刘氏清蒂，她子不叫目莲僧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫什么糖萝菔，醋萝菔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是傅罗卜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错，傅罗卜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请上城楼，我母子相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阎君知道，那还得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行个方便罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "使不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唵嘛呢叭咪吽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呦。哎呦。不要如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众鬼卒，将刘氏清蒂押上都城。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘氏上台子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一见母亲泪眼认，"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怎不叫人痛在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长官，将我母亲焰火去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众鬼卒，将刘氏清蒂焰火去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "刘清蒂站都城浑身颤抖，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罗卜，我儿，儿啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（回龙） 叫一声罗卜儿细听从头："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "儿本是阳世人相隔幽冥，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "却缘何来到了酆都城楼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "看不见小娇儿我两泪交流。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "竟变了那铁树开花不能保留。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "娘不该在阳间打僧骂道，不济贫民，开了五荤，到如今我此幽囚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄正板",
          "musical_style": "二黄正板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我的儿啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖缓锣鼓〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "儿的父修正道跨鹤西走，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "为娘我被阎君地府来收。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "又谁知到了阴曹，早晚间我受的是蓬头垢面，披枷带锁，口含阴灯，等何时我"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "才得出头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "也不枉为娘我就盼儿在心头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，今当四月初八日，阎君赴龙华大会去了。你可哀告掌关，放出都城，我"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母子也好相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘说道阴曹府报应无有"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿求佛尊将娘搭救"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长官，将我母亲放出都城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阎君知道，那还了得？使不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唵嘛呢叭咪吽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呦，哎呦，不必如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众鬼卒，将刘氏清蒂押出都城。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘氏走下，出城。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罗卜，我儿，儿啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "娘只说阴曹府无报应，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "天网恢恢有神灵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，为娘披枷带锁，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有佛法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快使来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "对准西方身拜定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "快将枷锁离娘身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为娘双目不明，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有佛法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快使来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "对准西方身拜定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "取来了甘露水付与娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "数载未见娇儿面，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "母子们相逢泪不干。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，为娘肚中饥饿，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有佛法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快使来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "对准西方身拜定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "取来了干饭付与娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众冤鬼同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，这些冤鬼，超度他们罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唵嘛呢叭咪吽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众冤鬼同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，这饭多被鬼抢了去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有佛法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快快使来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是，"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "二次又把身拜定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "目莲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "再取干饭付与娘亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小鬼上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阎君回殿来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你母子快快分别了罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说阎君回都城，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "母子就要两离分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘氏、目莲同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大鬼",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，且住。这些冤鬼俱已逃生去了。阎君回来，如何是好。也罢，待我也逃"
        }
      ],
